snippet.title: Sonic Frontiers: The Final Horizon Update Trailer
snippet.description:
The Sonic Frontiers: The Final Horizon Update will be available later today at 5pm Pacific! Rewrite your destiny with a new story, new playable characters, new challenges, and more in the climactic final content update...all for free!

Sonic Frontiers is available now: https://frontiers.sonicthehedgehog.com

Check out our other social pages to stay up to date on the latest Sonic happenings:

https://twitter.com/sonic_hedgehog
https://facebook.com/sonic
https://instagram.com/sonicthehedgehog
